{"tid":1516584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人！加油！","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T04:41:47.000Z","uid":145314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da5271177a13b419e39845ae085c138d429ec480","tid":1516584,"uid":145314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:16:54.000Z","msg":"我啊媽因為哩場運動而患上重度抑鬱症(Major depressive disorder) 佢周不時就會無端端喊。<br />\n<br />\n我問佢點解喊，有咩唔開心，佢一開始都話冇野，唔肯講，之後我再問佢，佢就話見到宜家既香港好唔開心，佢話冇諗過香港會變成咁。<br />\n<br />\n我平時都有發夢，但我開始覺得發夢冇乜用，由6月到以家2個月，政府都冇點樣正面回應過我地，我都覺得好攰啦，唔知點幫到香港。 <br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油啦！"},{"pid":"17feab0498fb3bbf88e2ea75a44f7b8569d9d911","tid":1516584,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"5ff9b09bfd6cfccbde3235c38146b7075a43047e","tid":1516584,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"謝謝你媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb55793d47353f83af312133c11ac0576ba6b61","tid":1516584,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:46.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"d3849959e9aef07b621ee2cf6112594f28c6ed93","tid":1516584,"uid":145314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"唉 好心酸"}]}